<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 18:08:29 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>战争中的以色列：您需要了解的信息 – 第 151 天</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-03-05/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-151/0000018e-0fa4-db19-abae-7fae6d6c0000</link><description>布林肯：有机会立即停火，由哈马斯决定是否准备好参与其中 ■ 美国、约旦向加沙北部空投援助物资 ■ 世界卫生组织：加沙北部的营养不良“特别严重” ■ 两枚火箭弹黎巴嫩袭击了以色列北部的建筑物 ■ 内塔尼亚胡：以色列将在斋月期间“尽一切努力维护阿克萨清真寺的礼拜自由” ■ 战争结束 151 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 17:46:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-03-05/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-151/0000018e-0fa4-db19-abae-7fae6d6c0000</guid></item><item><title>美国制裁间谍软件公司背后的前以色列情报官员</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-03-05/ty-article/.premium/u-s-sanctions-former-israeli-intel-officer-behind-spyware-firms/0000018e-0f97-d343-a9de-2ff7cf830000</link><description>美国财政部对 Intellexa Consortium 的以色列创始人实施制裁，原因是该公司在开发和销售“用于针对美国人的商业间谍软件技术”方面发挥了作用</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 17:24:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-03-05/ty-article/.premium/u-s-sanctions-former-israeli-intel-officer-behind-spyware-firms/0000018e-0f97-d343-a9de-2ff7cf830000</guid></item><item><title>如何根据社交媒体帖子创建 10 月 7 日存档？四位以色列历史学家正在寻找答案</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-05/ty-article-magazine/.premium/how-do-you-create-an-october-7-archive-from-social-media-four-historians-are-finding-out/0000018e-0f5b-d203-a9ce-1ffb67440000</link><description>特拉维夫大学博士生的一个新项目旨在记录黑色星期六的证词以及民间社会随后的反应，以确保官方的国家叙述不是未来唯一可以讲述的叙述。随之而来的是许多独特的挑战</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 17:12:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-05/ty-article-magazine/.premium/how-do-you-create-an-october-7-archive-from-social-media-four-historians-are-finding-out/0000018e-0f5b-d203-a9ce-1ffb67440000</guid></item><item><title>“内塔尼亚胡希望世界指责以色列的种族灭绝、种族隔离和种族清洗”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-03-05/ty-article-podcast/netanyahu-wants-the-world-to-accuse-israel-of-genocide-apartheid-and-ethnic-cleansing/0000018e-0f0f-d203-a9ce-1fbf16dc0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 16:54:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-03-05/ty-article-podcast/netanyahu-wants-the-world-to-accuse-israel-of-genocide-apartheid-and-ethnic-cleansing/0000018e-0f0f-d203-a9ce-1fbf16dc0000</guid></item><item><title>这座与加沙接壤的以色列城市的孩子们在战争中返回学校，感到恐惧和焦虑</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-05/ty-article-magazine/.premium/still-afraid-children-of-this-israeli-city-bordering-gaza-return-to-school-amidst-war/0000018e-0efa-dc50-a7af-1efbf4390000</link><description>斯德洛特市的学校自 10 月 7 日哈马斯袭击以来首次于周日重新开放，但对许多学生来说，即使是一次无辜的谈话也会让人痛苦地想起创伤。一位母亲说：“我希望政府知道它正在做什么让我们回到这里”</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 16:32:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-05/ty-article-magazine/.premium/still-afraid-children-of-this-israeli-city-bordering-gaza-return-to-school-amidst-war/0000018e-0efa-dc50-a7af-1efbf4390000</guid></item><item><title>以色列教育部长任命右翼内塔尼亚胡同事进入国家图书馆理事会</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-05/ty-article/.premium/education-minister-moves-to-appoint-netanyahu-associates-to-israels-national-library/0000018e-0f02-d917-adce-ef0e56330000</link><description>近年来，以色列国家机构政治化的尝试屡屡失败，教育部长约夫·基什 (Yoav Kisch) 寻求任命两名不合格的以色列国家图书馆理事会成员</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 16:08:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-05/ty-article/.premium/education-minister-moves-to-appoint-netanyahu-associates-to-israels-national-library/0000018e-0f02-d917-adce-ef0e56330000</guid></item><item><title>以色列议会委员会主席拒绝向国家监督机构提供有关哈马斯 10 月 7 日袭击事件的会议纪要</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-05/ty-article/.premium/knesset-committee-head-refuses-to-give-state-watchdog-minutes-relating-oct-7-attack/0000018e-0eb9-df9f-ad8e-9fbb152f0000</link><description>国家审计长马塔尼亚胡·恩格曼 (Matanyahu Englman) 寻求委员会记录，以确定该小组在 10 月 7 日之前向政府和军方发出的指令是否得到遵守，但议会没有义务满足国家审计长的要求</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 15:20:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-05/ty-article/.premium/knesset-committee-head-refuses-to-give-state-watchdog-minutes-relating-oct-7-attack/0000018e-0eb9-df9f-ad8e-9fbb152f0000</guid></item><item><title>在被指控存在反以色列偏见后，BBC 将联合制作新星节大屠杀纪录片</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2024-03-05/ty-article/.premium/bbc-to-co-produce-nova-festival-massacre-documentary/0000018e-0ef9-d547-a19e-8ef97d3c0000</link><description>这家英国广播公司参与了这部名为《我们将再次跳舞》的电影，该电影基于采访和实时镜头，被指控反以色列报道，并拒绝将哈马斯定义为恐怖组织</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 15:03:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2024-03-05/ty-article/.premium/bbc-to-co-produce-nova-festival-massacre-documentary/0000018e-0ef9-d547-a19e-8ef97d3c0000</guid></item><item><title>美国终于意识到：内塔尼亚胡打破了牢不可破的联盟</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-05/ty-article/.premium/the-u-s-finally-realized-netanyahu-broke-an-unbreakable-alliance/0000018e-0df1-dc37-a9ae-dffba1cf0000</link><description>15年来，通过傲慢和粗鲁，本杰明·内塔尼亚胡成功地将以色列从一个盟友变成了一个难以维持的持续危机，其行为与美国在中东的利益不一致</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 14:00:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-05/ty-article/.premium/the-u-s-finally-realized-netanyahu-broke-an-unbreakable-alliance/0000018e-0df1-dc37-a9ae-dffba1cf0000</guid></item><item><title>“每个人都心碎”：加沙战争阴影下的耶路撒冷，斋月的喜悦变成了绝望</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-05/ty-article/.premium/everyone-is-heartbroken-ramadan-joy-turns-to-despair-in-jerusalem-under-wars-shadow/0000018e-0db4-d857-adff-cffd8e450000</link><description>由于有关圣殿山礼拜自由的决定尚未做出，往年熙熙攘攘的商店都关门了，传统装饰品仍留在储藏室里，老城的居民担心爆发疫情</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 12:41:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-05/ty-article/.premium/everyone-is-heartbroken-ramadan-joy-turns-to-despair-in-jerusalem-under-wars-shadow/0000018e-0db4-d857-adff-cffd8e450000</guid></item><item><title>与沙特阿拉伯的正常化将在加沙决定，但以色列并不着急</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-05/ty-article/.premium/normalization-with-saudi-arabia-will-be-decided-in-gaza-but-israels-in-no-hurry/0000018e-0e3e-dc37-a9ae-de7e3d230000</link><description>加沙战争之前，沙特寻求与以色列关系正常化，以换取美国同意沙特核计划以及利雅得与华盛顿之间的防务协定，但现在沙特首先需要找到加沙问题的解决方案</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 12:00:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-05/ty-article/.premium/normalization-with-saudi-arabia-will-be-decided-in-gaza-but-israels-in-no-hurry/0000018e-0e3e-dc37-a9ae-de7e3d230000</guid></item><item><title>土耳其又拘留了七名涉嫌向以色列摩萨德出售信息的人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2024-03-05/ty-article/turkey-detains-7-more-people-for-allegedly-selling-information-to-israels-mossad/0000018e-0e2f-d857-adff-cfffd8d40000</link><description>土耳其内政部长表示，被拘留者涉嫌收集土耳其个人和公司的数据并将其出售给以色列情报机构。 “我们永远不会允许在我国境内进行间谍活动”</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 10:50:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2024-03-05/ty-article/turkey-detains-7-more-people-for-allegedly-selling-information-to-israels-mossad/0000018e-0e2f-d857-adff-cfffd8d40000</guid></item><item><title>印度国民被确认为以色列北部导弹袭击的受害者；大使馆敦促国民寻求安全</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-05/ty-article/.premium/indian-national-identified-as-victim-of-missile-attack-at-northern-israel/0000018e-0e0f-d5ee-a78e-3ecfb62e0000</link><description>31 岁的帕塔尼宾·马克斯韦尔 (Patanibin Maxwell) 于 12 月抵达以色列，在以色列北部边境的玛格利奥社区从事农业工作。他身后留下了怀孕的妻子和五岁的儿子。他的两个兄弟在印度境外工作，其中一个在以色列</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 10:26:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-05/ty-article/.premium/indian-national-identified-as-victim-of-missile-attack-at-northern-israel/0000018e-0e0f-d5ee-a78e-3ecfb62e0000</guid></item><item><title>美国对以色列在加沙的失望已经转化为愤怒。哈马斯最先注意到</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-05/ty-article/.premium/as-the-humanitarian-crisis-in-gaza-escalates-u-s-patience-with-israel-is-running-out/0000018e-0ae5-d3bd-afce-bbe795eb0000</link><description>这一变化主要是由美国副总统呼吁立即停火发出的，哈马斯已经注意到了这一变化，哈马斯似乎在谈判中采取了更强硬的立场。除了内塔尼亚胡寻求政治生存之外，华盛顿正在努力确定以色列的战争战略</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 04:00:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-05/ty-article/.premium/as-the-humanitarian-crisis-in-gaza-escalates-u-s-patience-with-israel-is-running-out/0000018e-0ae5-d3bd-afce-bbe795eb0000</guid></item><item><title>几位利库德集团部长反对斯莫特里奇绕过法院裁决为犹太学院提供资金的计划</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-05/ty-article/.premium/several-likud-ministers-oppose-smotrichs-plan-to-bypass-court-ruling-to-fund-yeshivas/0000018e-0ae7-d857-adff-cfff11e60000</link><description>据以色列总检察长称，如果新的法律草案在 3 月底前未获得通过，犹太学院基金将被暂停。无论如何，FM Smotrich 为犹太学院提供资金的想法引起了利库德集团部长们的愤怒，他们认为这会因对正统征兵豁免的愤怒而引起公众的愤怒</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 04:00:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-05/ty-article/.premium/several-likud-ministers-oppose-smotrichs-plan-to-bypass-court-ruling-to-fund-yeshivas/0000018e-0ae7-d857-adff-cfff11e60000</guid></item><item><title>以色列士兵在约旦河西岸持刀袭击中受重伤；拜登：停火在哈马斯手中</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-05/ty-article-live/u-s-vp-harris-urges-humanitarian-plan-before-any-rafah-action-in-meeting-with-gantz/0000018e-0c97-d5ee-a78e-3cd7db650000</link><description>约旦、美国空投食品、向加沙北部提供援助 ■ 埃及媒体称，加沙谈判尽管困难重重仍将恢复；布林肯表示，有机会立即停火，由哈马斯决定 ■ 半岛电视台报道真主党向以色列军事基地开火 ■ 甘茨表示，他在美国会谈期间“强调了在加沙建立国际政府的重要性” ■ 以色列国防军摧毁了加沙最大的隧道尚未揭开；导致以色列埃雷兹过境点 ■ 巴勒斯坦官员称，以色列对汗尤尼斯的袭击造成 17 人死亡</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 03:16:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-05/ty-article-live/u-s-vp-harris-urges-humanitarian-plan-before-any-rafah-action-in-meeting-with-gantz/0000018e-0c97-d5ee-a78e-3cd7db650000</guid></item><item><title>联合国报告发现哈马斯 10 月 7 日袭击、人质事件中以色列受害者的“性暴力和强奸的明确证据”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-05/ty-article/.premium/un-report-clear-evidence-of-sexual-violence-rape-during-and-after-hamas-oct-7-attack/0000018e-0b47-d3bd-afce-bbc7a2ac0000</link><description>以色列欢迎“最终承认”哈马斯的性犯罪，但拒绝调查巴勒斯坦有关以色列人性暴力的指控</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 22:09:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-05/ty-article/.premium/un-report-clear-evidence-of-sexual-violence-rape-during-and-after-hamas-oct-7-attack/0000018e-0b47-d3bd-afce-bbc7a2ac0000</guid></item><item><title>当甘茨和加兰特挑战内塔尼亚胡时，掌握总理权力的不仅仅是极右派</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-04/ty-article/.premium/as-gantz-gallant-defy-netanyahu-its-not-just-the-far-right-that-hold-power-over-the-pm/0000018e-0b13-d9cb-afdf-0b9fe0070000</link><description>甘茨对白宫的流氓访问和加兰特对法案草案的强硬否决，为内阁成员针对内塔尼亚胡的叛变开启了新的篇章。由于紧急“团结”政府，总理的极右翼盟友并不是唯一能够瓦解联盟的人</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 21:10:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-04/ty-article/.premium/as-gantz-gallant-defy-netanyahu-its-not-just-the-far-right-that-hold-power-over-the-pm/0000018e-0b13-d9cb-afdf-0b9fe0070000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡要求将腐败审判的证词推迟到战后</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-04/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-asks-to-postpone-testimonies-in-corruption-trial-until-after-war/0000018e-0aa7-d5ee-a78e-3ae716790000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡的律师向法庭提出动议，要求“只要国家安全局势没有实质性变化”就推迟作证，理由是加沙战争导致总理与其法律团队之间沟通困难。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 19:44:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-04/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-asks-to-postpone-testimonies-in-corruption-trial-until-after-war/0000018e-0aa7-d5ee-a78e-3ae716790000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国家委员会关于梅龙山灾难的报告将于本周发布</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-04/ty-article/.premium/israeli-state-commission-report-on-mount-meron-disaster-to-be-released-this-week/0000018e-0ac9-d857-adff-cff946cf0000</link><description>2021 年 4 月，以色列北部梅龙山的 Lag B&amp;#39;Omer 庆祝活动期间发生人群拥挤事件，造成 45 人死亡。调查委员会询问了包括总理内塔尼亚胡和警察局长在内的证人，并警告说“他们可能会受到该报告的影响”</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 19:39:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-04/ty-article/.premium/israeli-state-commission-report-on-mount-meron-disaster-to-be-released-this-week/0000018e-0ac9-d857-adff-cff946cf0000</guid></item></channel></rss>